21 State Settlement Cash Fund to the Legal Education for Public Service and
22 Rural Practice Loan Repayment Assistance Fund on the operative date of
23 this section, or as soon thereafter as administratively possible.
24 Sec. 43. Section 84-941.01, Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, is
25 amended to read:
